523
00:45:20,876 --> 00:45:22,502
Dengar, Eun!

524
00:45:22,586 --> 00:45:25,881
<i>Jangan coba menyalahkanku! Beraninya kau!</i>

525
00:45:25,964 --> 00:45:29,384
Jika kau menyentuh agen kami,

526
00:45:29,468 --> 00:45:31,929
