529
00:45:40,729 --> 00:45:42,064
Mengerti?

530
00:46:04,962 --> 00:46:07,339
<i>Jadi, Soo-hyeok sudah ditangkap?</i>

531
00:46:20,394 --> 00:46:21,270
Kau memanggilku?

532
00:46:21,353 --> 00:46:23,605
Sebentar lagi kita ke Universitas Hosu.

533
00:46:23,689 --> 00:46:24,898
Dengan pengamanan penuh.

534
00:46:27,276 --> 00:46:28,569
Eun Chang-su sendiri?

535
00:46:29,236 --> 00:46:30,862
