00:55:27,983 --> 00:55:29,359
-Aku tak boleh bergerak! Tidak!
-Tunggu!

652
00:55:30,277 --> 00:55:31,403
Tidak!

653
00:55:42,581 --> 00:55:43,665
Astaga.

654
00:55:49,171 --> 00:55:52,507
Berengsek! Kenapa kau mengencingiku?

655
00:56:02,809 --> 00:56:03,685
Kau.

656
00:56:06,438 --> 00:56:07,606
Pergi ke pintu depan.

657
00:56:19,618 --> 00:56:20,744
Ikut dengannya.

658
00:56:28,001 --> 00:56:29,002
Tetap di sini.

659
00:56:29,086 --> 00:56:30,170
Baik, Tuan.

660
00:56:41,557 --> 00:56:44,685
Sial! Bedebah itu!

661
00:56:45,269 --> 00:56:46,478
<i>Saat ini,</i>

662
00:56:46,979 --> 00:56:48,605
<i>kemari dan ambil telepon lapangan.</i>

663
00:56:49,106 --> 00:56:50,274
<i>Lim Soo-ho.</i>

664
00:56:51,149 --> 00:56:52,526
<i>Kuperingatkan kau lagi...</i>

665
00:57:01,785 --> 00:57:03,620
Kau akan melihat telepon di luar.

666
00:57:03,704 --> 00:57:05,080
Ambil itu.

667
00:57:07,958 --> 00:57:08,959
Apa?

668
00:57:10,085 --> 00:57:11,628
Maksudmu, aku?

669
00:57:14,381 --> 00:57:16,884
Jika lakukan hal bodoh, pacarmu akan mati.

670
00:57:22,848 --> 00:57:23,682
Gwang-tae.

671
00:57:27,436 --> 00:57:28,770
Aku mencintaimu.

672
00:57:30,272 --> 00:57:32,065
Kau satu-satunya untukku.

673
00:57:32,649 --> 00:57:33,734
Kau tahu itu, bukan?

674
00:57:33,817 --> 00:57:35,652
Ini tidak akan sulit.

675
00:57:35,736 --> 00:57:38,280
Berjalanlah perlahan ke sana
dan bawa kemari.

676
00:57:38,363 --> 00:57:39,406
Mengerti?

677
00:57:40,449 --> 00:57:41,867
Ambil sekarang!

678
00:57:43,118 --> 00:57:44,161
Sekarang.

679
00:57:55,797 --> 00:57:57,716
ORANG LUAR DILARANG MASUK

680
00:58:03,639 --> 00:58:04,473
Ada yang keluar.

681
00:58:05,182 --> 00:58:06,725
Angkat perisai kalian.

682
00:58:23,033 --> 00:58:24,159
Itu bukan Lim Soo-ho.

683
00:58:25,619 --> 00:58:27,162
Kurasa dia mahasiswa.

684
00:58:29,456 --> 00:58:30,541
<i>Baiklah.</i>

685
00:58:31,542 --> 00:58:32,793
<i>Jangan khawatir.</i>

686
00:58:33,710 --> 00:58:36,713
<i>Kami takkan menembakmu.</i>

687
00:58:37,714 --> 00:58:38,924
<i>Perlahan,</i>

688
00:58:39,466 --> 00:58:41,260
<i>ambil teleponnya dan kembali ke dalam.</i>

689
00:58:51,603 --> 00:58:54,147
Gwang-tae, ayo!

690
00:59:08,328 --> 00:59:09,872
Lim Soo-ho ada di balik pintu.

691
00:59:09,955 --> 00:59:10,789
Benarkah?

692
00:59:51,371 --> 00:59:52,748
Siapa yang menembakkan pistol?

693
01:00:04,509 --> 01:00:07,304
Tahan tembakan!

694
01:00:14,728 --> 01:00:17,731
Kita tidak boleh menembak mereka.
