695
01:00:20,943 --> 01:00:24,529
Angkat! Lalu turunkan. Rendahkan tubuhmu!

696
01:00:24,613 --> 01:00:25,989
Angkat perisainya!

697
01:00:26,365 --> 01:00:27,324
Jangan tembak.

698
01:00:27,407 --> 01:00:28,534
Beri tahu mereka untuk tak balas menembak.

699
01:00:28,617 --> 01:00:30,786
Jangan balas menembak. Tahan tembakan!

700
01:00:32,663 --> 01:00:33,664
Ambil sekarang.

701
01:00:35,624 --> 01:00:38,210
Angkat perisainya!

702
01:00:41,421 --> 01:00:43,590
Baiklah. Mundur!

703
01:00:43,715 --> 01:00:45,384
-Mundur!
